cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.IR

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with learning sentence vectors from an unlabeled corpus. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it proposes novel sentence vector learning algorithms. Additionally, since the paper discusses the use of sentence vectors in natural language processing tasks, it could also be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
